(fields=id,name,users[*]) request\nidentical data -- the only difference is expansion syntax -- so post-fix\nthey must cost the same, not merely \"not catastrophically worse\". The\nprevious lt(20_000) gave wildcard its own generous independent margin\n(derived from having no clean pre-fix baseline for it, since baseline\nwildcard requests timed out 10/10 at Gatling's 60s client limit) rather\nthan anchoring on bare's own clean, real baseline measurement (9,057ms).\nThat let a wildcard-specific regression up to ~3x bare's own cost pass\nsilently -- exactly the failure mode this test exists to catch. Wildcard\nnow shares bare's threshold (lt(8_700)), so any divergence between the two\nis caught at the same point, directly enforcing the equivalence that is\nthis test's actual regression signal.","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"df4d02efafa210d968dd45167f12a6fc86520748","tree_id":"4184feb335f19bee6ecd786f1655c38de9c11246","timestamp":"2026-07-22T18:53:15Z","committer":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"http